{"tid":1280609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家幫我推畀Andrew.","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T12:17:54.000Z","uid":266607,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"493fb0556cc060aa6c1d84398ac7b819e7308cb0","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"請大家幫我推畀Andrew.<br />\n<br />\nAndrew.<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n我只係希望你試下思考一個問題：如果你而家見到當時企係PP天台的梁凌杰。你會做什麼？<br />\n<br />\n我會拉住佢。攬住佢。唔會畀佢去死。<br />\n<br />\n我同朋友睇左好多次梁凌杰墮樓時的畫面。佢一直一直用力握住大廈外圍的工程支架。他不想死。他根本不想死。他想求生！<br />\n<br />\n我大膽推測，如果當時不是大量持盾的警察在場包圍。如果勸說的不是警方的談判專家而是我們的手足。如果他擁有「不被捕就能安全離開」的選擇。他根本絕對不會以這個方式下到地面。<br />\n<br />\n我激憤難平。我不要我再有任何一個兄弟和姊妹受傷。這個政府的罪惡罄竹難書。<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n我今時今日之所以仲有力量。唔係因為我覺得個政府有救。唔係因為我覺得警察會變好。唔係因為我覺得果啲既得利益者們會收手﹑會良心發現。<br />\n而係因為我見到呢2,000,000人。見到捨身衝入立法會的兄弟。見到返轉頭抬走死士的姊妹。仲有協助所有人撤退的市民同記者。七月一日深夜的全體大撤退真係諗起幾多次都想喊。我的內心亦因而得著無窮的力量。我感到我被愛。我感到我被珍視。我知道我們在同行。我們並不孤單。<br />\n<br />\n我好希望三位離開的手足也能和我和你一樣，親身分享這幅充滿愛和幸福的畫景。世界並沒有希望。希望在我們的兄弟姊妹身上。<br />\n<br />\n當我知道，世界有呢2,000,000人的存在。我已經唔再需要自己一個驚到覺得除左死之外沒有路可以行。他/她們身上有我的道路。<br />\n<br />\n如果，這份巨大的愛情能夠更早地展示出來。他們就不需要走上絕路。<br />\n<br />\n請你不要被擊倒。<br />\n不要被無力感擊倒。<br />\n不要被惡人擊倒。<br />\n從這一刻開始。就由我們自己。來停止這一串自殺骨牌。<br />\n不要再讓它帶走我們當中任何一個人。<br />\n親者痛。仇者快。<br />\n<br />\n我們一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n2019-0703"},{"pid":"8be4fd0515f7a608909a74b5098d4e763d769345","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"457e3d560905d599a795153cdea6515c96846130","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"c9b2373f5d731d265429fbe98c1a9cc670c9aaeb","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"3f782239a1daea61061114b474c01caa1e6e7ace","tid":1280609,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"093c514880b0c056e60f4d430f8c2fb8bc8388b1","tid":1280609,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3556a2877c8a3b74d2f1d9f79a0ed68caac4449","tid":1280609,"uid":272964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"8043ec1bf74e3c2fc57642eb39071b0bca6f751d","tid":1280609,"uid":246243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1de77ae1bca6c98c506684103e5d93fd68cd5477","tid":1280609,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>我認為「想掩蓋愚昧這事實，最好的方法就是表現出氾濫的同情心」<br />\n<br />\n逆向操作是「只要表現有氾濫的同情心，就可以操縱愚昧的事物」<br />\n<br />\n有人打電話同你講「你屋企人而家係大陸犯咗法拘留緊，快點過數到指定帳戶才放人」你都唔會諗都唔諗，寧願先相信。<br />\n<br />\n叫你小心啲，又被指摘為「冷血」，這個世道真奇怪，難怪好人難做，妖魔鬼怪多僧道。<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想再有殉國烈士，亦不想大家的同情心被利用和消磨，令真正需要人被忽略！！</strong>"},{"pid":"b33407b3492f6d9e7c385ab837a2db984009cbb1","tid":1280609,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢搵番未？"},{"pid":"c492d1c6344fd83846c653def148903028eed123","tid":1280609,"uid":252193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e3eede5490eb3b4c14f6290ce30de30193f0a80","tid":1280609,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"Andrew <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Please come back to us<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ac42563fcd82effac00bd7af7cdf02d25038cf","tid":1280609,"uid":229269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1d3da4ea72403fe7c075a7763b487870c55ca91","tid":1280609,"uid":241715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:07:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deb80fb245530331fe96c49ed2ffe407380014e4","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:32:45.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ce71849c668ea214dcac7dd6fe614b365da083e4","tid":1280609,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"幫你推 大家都幫手推"},{"pid":"f8184842efbdbf9088a6b80004ef14cbd6816129","tid":1280609,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"唔好離開我哋"},{"pid":"c9af0f696ae874a6c30c575a9f6ae41d18b70541","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"221b30f0d41c78ca5405f1e0cfa32c5abab6e24b","tid":1280609,"uid":272509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab134efe3730320ccc345c827ced25fe48a9b5df","tid":1280609,"uid":59450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"[幫推thx]招人一齊喺政總跪<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ddNvkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ddNvkT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n相同的心😢希望救到一個得一個"},{"pid":"a7e677673dbf882df966682d2f7d62a945615cf9","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"up."},{"pid":"6eeb6dd38abc2281e235d1c87ae776c5ac35b337","tid":1280609,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"up"}]}